# password.yab
# Password program using repeat and if
answer$ = "42"
Input "What is the password? " pass$
If (pass$ = answer$) Then
Print "You got it right! Have a cookie ^^"
End
Endif
If (pass$ <> answer$) Then
Repeat
Input "Incorrect password, please try again: " pass$
Until (pass$ = answer$)
Print "You got it right! Have a cookie ^^"
Endif